@page "/faq"

<PageTitle>FAQ | EasySystems</PageTitle>

<div class="faq-page">

    <section class="faq-hero">
        <p class="eyebrow">FAQ</p>
        <h1>Frequently asked questions</h1>
        <p>Answers to common questions about online stores, pricing, delivery, and support.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How do I start?</h3>
            <p>Create an account, choose a package, and submit your store request.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How long does delivery take?</h3>
            <p>Starter usually takes around 7 days, Business around 14 days, and Premium depends on project scope.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Can I update my request later?</h3>
            <p>Yes. You can contact us or follow updates through your dashboard.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Do you support multiple languages?</h3>
            <p>Yes. We can build stores in Swedish, Arabic, English, or multiple languages.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Do you help after launch?</h3>
            <p>Yes. Support is available depending on the package and agreement.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Can I get a custom solution?</h3>
            <p>Yes. Premium and custom projects can include special features and integrations.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

</div>